Name: Government Service Channel
Description: A means of delivering a government service to the intended audience.

Properties.Name: Available language
Properties.Description: A language that may be used to access the service channel.

Properties.Name: Estimated processing time
Properties.Description: The estimated processing time of the service through this channel.

Properties.Name: Mailing address access
Properties.Description: The address where forms may be sent to access the service.

Properties.Name: Phone access
Properties.Description: The telephone number where the service may be accessed.

Properties.Name: Physical location access
Properties.Description: The physical location where the service can be accessed.

Properties.Name: SMS access
Properties.Description: The SMS number where the service can be accessed.

Properties.Name: Website access
Properties.Description: The website where the service may be accessed.
